<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('../partials/head', { title }) %></head>
<body class="page-ecosystem">
<%- include('../partials/header', { activePage }) %>

<main class="eco-main">
  <section class="eco-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eco-pill">OUR VISION</span>
      <h1>The Moovex Ecosystem</h1>
      <p class="eco-lead">
        Building a circular, tech-enabled network of ventures that drive sustainable development
        and entrepreneurial excellence across Zambia.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="eco-definition">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eco-definition-card">
        <div class="eco-definition-body">
          <h2>What is the Moovex ecosystem?</h2>
          <p>
            It is a synchronized network of specialized companies designed to solve local challenges
            through practical innovation. By connecting energy, digital services, retail, finance access,
            and property management, Moovex creates a fertile ground where businesses thrive and
            communities prosper.
          </p>
          <div class="eco-definition-note">
            <span class="eco-definition-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6.05 8.05a7 7 0 1010.9 0A7 7 0 006.05 8.05zM4 10a9 9 0 1116 0 9 9 0 01-16 0zm8-3.5a1.5 1.5 0 110 3 1.5 1.5 0 010-3z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Sustainably Powered Growth</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-definition-watermark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="120" height="120" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 014 4v1h3a2 2 0 012 2v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V9a2 2 0 012-2h3V6a4 4 0 014-4zm0 2a2 2 0 00-2 2v1h4V6a2 2 0 00-2-2zm-5 5v11h10V9H7z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.35"/></svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="eco-hub" aria-labelledby="eco-hub-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eco-hub-heading">
        <h2 id="eco-hub-title">Our Strategic Pillars</h2>
        <p>Moovex Central Hub</p>
      </div>

      <div class="eco-hub-stack" aria-label="Moovex ecosystem diagram with Moovex at the center connected to Chomaya, GetPro, Facha, Netra, and future companies">
        <article class="eco-hub-center eco-soft-shadow">
          <div class="eco-hub-core-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 2.38 1.19 4.47 3 5.74V17a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-2.26c1.81-1.27 3-3.36 3-5.74 0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 2c2.76 0 5 2.24 5 5s-2.24 5-5 5-5-2.24-5-5 2.24-5 5-5zm-3 12v-1h6v1H9z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Moovex</h3>
          <p>Ecosystem Core</p>
        </article>

        <div class="eco-hub-spokes">
          <a href="/portfolio#chomaya" class="eco-spoke eco-glass-card eco-soft-shadow">
            <div class="eco-spoke-icon eco-spoke-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M6 3h12v2H6V3zm0 4h12l-1 10H7L6 7zm2 12h8v2H8v-2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Chomaya</h4>
              <p>Microfuel and fuel-management for PSV drivers, taxis, buses, and transport operators</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/portfolio#getpro" class="eco-spoke eco-glass-card eco-soft-shadow">
            <div class="eco-spoke-icon eco-spoke-icon-teal" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 006 0V4a3 3 0 00-3-3zm7 11v2a7 7 0 01-14 0v-2H3v2a9 9 0 0018 0v-2h-2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>GetPro</h4>
              <p>Call center and digital agency for customer service, websites, apps, and social media</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/portfolio#facha" class="eco-spoke eco-glass-card eco-soft-shadow">
            <div class="eco-spoke-icon eco-spoke-icon-green" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 10v10h16V10H4zm2 2h12v6H6v-6zm2-6h8v2H8V6zm2-4h4v2h-4V2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Facha</h4>
              <p>Stationery, internet café, wholesale drinks, and e-banking for Airtel, MTN, Zamtel, and banks</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/portfolio#netra" class="eco-spoke eco-glass-card eco-soft-shadow">
            <div class="eco-spoke-icon eco-spoke-icon-blue" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 7V3H2v18h20V7H12zm-2 12H4v-2h6v2zm0-4H4v-2h6v2zm0-4H4V9h6v2zm8 8h-6v-2h6v2zm0-4h-6v-2h6v2zm0-4h-6V9h6v2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Netra</h4>
              <p>Commercial property management for shopping complexes — operations, tenants, traffic, and revenue</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/partner" class="eco-spoke eco-spoke-future eco-soft-shadow">
            <div class="eco-spoke-icon eco-spoke-icon-muted" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 13h-6v6h-2v-6H5v-2h6V5h2v6h6v2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Future Companies</h4>
              <p>More ventures joining the Moovex network over time</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="eco-benefits">
    <div class="container eco-benefits-grid">
      <article class="eco-benefit-block">
        <div class="eco-benefit-heading eco-benefit-heading-green">
          <span class="eco-benefit-bar"></span>
          <h3>How companies benefit</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-benefit-list">
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-check" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Integrated Logistics</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Access to seamless energy and transport networks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-check" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Digital First Infrastructure</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Enterprise-grade tech tools tailored for the local market.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-check" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Shared Prosperity Model</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Collective collaboration and shared resources across the Moovex network.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="eco-benefit-block">
        <div class="eco-benefit-heading eco-benefit-heading-orange">
          <span class="eco-benefit-bar"></span>
          <h3>How society benefits</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="eco-benefit-list">
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-icon-wrap eco-benefit-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3s-1.34-3-3-3-3 1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5C15 14.17 10.33 13 8 13zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Employment Creation</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Jobs and livelihoods generated through connected ventures across Zambia.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-icon-wrap eco-benefit-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Financial Inclusion</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Bringing banking and digital services to underserved rural areas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-benefit-item">
            <span class="eco-benefit-icon-wrap eco-benefit-icon-orange" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 3L1 12h3v8h6v-6h2v6h6v-8h3L12 3zm0 2.8L17 12h-2v6h-2v-6H9.8L12 5.8z"></path></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="eco-benefit-title">Skill Transfer</p>
              <p class="eco-benefit-desc">Continuous training and incubation for local entrepreneurs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<a href="/partner" class="eco-fab" aria-label="Partner with Moovex">
  <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20 6h-2V4a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h16a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2zM8 4h8v2H8V4zm-1 9h2v2H7v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2z"></path></svg>
</a>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
